title: Wildfires in the West
lede: The Bogus Creek Fire burns in the Yukon Delta National Wildlife Refuge in southwest Alaska, June 7, 2015. The 25,260-acre fire, now extinguished, was reportedly started by lightning on May 31, 2015.
